title: Wall Street Breakfast: The Week Ahead
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Investors hone in on inflation and the Federal Reserve, Peloton Interactive (NASDAQ:PTON) shares tumble to an all-time low , and the rough ride for electric vehicle stocks continues, as Tesla’s (TSLA) Elon Musk gets set to speak at a major car summit this week.
